definition: abbr. for 克羅地亞|克罗地亚[Ke4 luo2 di4 ya4], Croatia/(Tw) abbr. for 克羅埃西亞|克罗埃西亚[Ke4 luo2 ai1 xi1 ya4], Croatia
Slovakia/Slovak/abbr. for 斯洛伐克[Si1 luo4 fa2 ke4]

sentences.english: By the seventh day, Felix, accepting his fate, no longer begged for mercy.
sentences.chinese: 第七天，費利克斯認命了，不再祈求寬恕。

sentences.english: Feliks gently lifted the bottle of nitroglycerine out of the sink.
sentences.chinese: 費利克斯輕輕地從水池中拿起那瓶硝化甘油。

sentences.english: Now this is not to say that Felix wasn't trying his best.
sentences.chinese: 現在不能說費利克斯沒有盡最大努力。

sentences.english: Felix de Weldon died in two thousand three.
sentences.chinese: 費利克斯死於德韋爾登兩千三。

sentences.english: Feliks went to the bar and asked for a glass of ale and a cold sausage .
sentences.chinese: 費利克斯直走到櫃檯，要了一杯啤酒，一盤涼香腸。

sentences.english: It is the fourth planet in orbit around the star Felix.
sentences.chinese: 它是圍繞恆星費利克斯旋轉的第四顆行星。

sentences.english: They have tracked the man feliks to his lodging .
sentences.chinese: 他們跟蹤那個費利克斯到了他的住處。

sentences.english: Feliks saw the crest on the back of the envelope.
sentences.chinese: 費利克斯看了看信封背面的頂飾。

sentences.english: Felix de Weldon wanted to make sure he had them correct.
sentences.chinese: 費利克斯德韋爾登希望確保他有這些正確的。

sentences.english: The man gave a shout of surprise and then Feliks had him by the throat .
sentences.chinese: 那個人喫驚地喊了一聲，費利克斯掐住了他的喉嚨。

sentences.english: Felix went to that great lily pad in the sky.
sentences.chinese: 費利克斯到天堂中的那片大睡蓮浮葉上去了。

sentences.english: A peculiar feeling came over Feliks.
sentences.chinese: 一種特殊的情感傳遍費利克斯全身。

sentences.english: 'A what?' said Cuthbert and Felix both.
sentences.chinese: “你說什麼呀？”卡斯伯特和費利克斯一齊問。

sentences.english: The air became cooler but Feliks perspired all the same.
sentences.chinese: 空氣涼爽了，但費利克斯仍然渾身出汗。

sentences.english: I can offer you now ten percent more than Felix did.
sentences.chinese: 我可以向你現在的百分之十比費利克斯多一些。

sentences.english: Feliks' heart sank: he had not expected them to be that smart.
sentences.chinese: 費利克斯心中一涼，他沒想到他們能這麼狡猾。
